definitions.definition: Coquettish behaviour; actions designed to excite erotic attention, without intending to reciprocate such feelings (chiefly of women towards men); flirtatious teasing .
An act constituting such behaviour; an affectation of amorous interest or enticement, especially of a woman directed towards a man.
